      <title>晶片製造商 AMD 第一季營收超出預期</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/chipmaker-amd-beats-first-quarter-revenue-estimates-2024-04-30/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[晶片製造商 Advanced Micro Devices 週二第一季營收小幅超出預期，原因是傳統資料中心使用的晶片需求不溫不火，加劇了遊戲晶片市場的疲軟。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/chipmaker-amd-beats-first-quarter-revenue-estimates-2024-04-30/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 20:23:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>馬斯克解散特斯拉電動車充電團隊，讓客戶蒙在鼓裡</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/musk-disbands-tesla-ev-charging-team-leaving-customers-dark-2024-04-30/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[產業官員和分析師週二表示，馬斯克突然決定解僱負責特斯拉電動車充電業務的員工，這讓那些準備為客戶配備新電動車以使用特斯拉超級充電網路的汽車製造商措手不及。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/musk-disbands-tesla-ev-charging-team-leaving-customers-dark-2024-04-30/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 20:23:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>億滋國際超越第一季銷售額和利潤預期</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/mondelez-international-beats-q1-sales-profit-estimates-2024-04-30/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[吉百利母公司億滋國際(Mondelez International)週二的第一季銷售額和利潤超出了市場預期，儘管通膨成本不斷上升，但得益於對其巧克力和鹹餅乾等昂貴產品的穩定需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/mondelez-international-beats-q1-sales-profit-estimates-2024-04-30/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 20:14:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由於天然氣價格仍然較低，切薩皮克能源公司季度利潤未達預期</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/chesapeake-energy-misses-quarterly-profit-estimates-natgas-prices-remain-low-2024-04-30/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[天然氣生產商切薩皮克能源公司(Chesapeake Energy Corp)週二第一季利潤未達到華爾街預期，因為持續走低的天然氣價格拖累了該公司的營收。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/chesapeake-energy-misses-quarterly-profit-estimates-natgas-prices-remain-low-2024-04-30/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 20:12:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>星巴克報告季度銷售額意外下降</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/starbucks-reports-surprise-fall-quarterly-sales-2024-04-30/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[星巴克週二公佈第二季可比銷售額意外下降，因為其兩個最大市場美國和中國的咖啡需求疲軟，導致其股價在盤後交易中下跌 6%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/starbucks-reports-surprise-fall-quarterly-sales-2024-04-30/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 20:10:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Pinterest 預測季度營收高於預期，股價飆升</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/pinterest-forecasts-quarterly-revenue-above-estimates-robust-ad-spend-2024-04-30/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Pinterest 週二預測第二季營收將高於華爾街預期，預計該圖片共享平台廣告支出的成長將推動其股價在盤後交易中上漲 20% 以上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/pinterest-forecasts-quarterly-revenue-above-estimates-robust-ad-spend-2024-04-30/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 20:08:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亞馬遜預測季度營收低於預期</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/amazon-forecasts-quarterly-revenue-below-estimates-2024-04-30/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亞馬遜週二預測第二季營收低於華爾街預期，因為該公司預計注重成本的企業在其雲端運算服務上的支出將不溫不火。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/amazon-forecasts-quarterly-revenue-below-estimates-2024-04-30/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 20:04:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳洲西太平洋銀行將暫停關閉地區分行的期限延長至 2027 年</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/australian-bank-westpac-extends-moratorium-regional-branch-closures-till-2027-2024-04-30/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[西太平洋銀行 (Westpac Banking Corp) 週三稍早表示，已將其地區分行的關閉時間至少推遲到 2027 年，並將在未來兩年內投資超過 1.5 億澳元來改善這些分行的服務。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/australian-bank-westpac-extends-moratorium-regional-branch-closures-till-2027-2024-04-30/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 19:41:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美國FCC恢復對寬頻服務供應商的全面監管</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/media-telecom/us-fcc-resumes-oversight-over-broadband-providers-cancelling-2017-memo-2024-04-30/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美國聯邦通訊委員會 (FCC) 週二表示，它已終止與聯邦貿易委員會 2017 年簽署的諒解備忘錄，該備忘錄改變了對寬頻服務提供者的部分監管。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/media-telecom/us-fcc-resumes-oversight-over-broadband-providers-cancelling-2017-memo-2024-04-30/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 19:32:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
