      <title>隨著美國司法部將大麻重新歸類為危險性較低的藥物，大麻股上漲</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/pot-stocks-jump-us-doj-moves-reclassify-cannabis-less-dangerous-drug-2024-04-30/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美國司法部（DoJ）採取行動將大麻重新歸類為危險性較低的藥物後，大麻公司的股價週二下午飆升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/pot-stocks-jump-us-doj-moves-reclassify-cannabis-less-dangerous-drug-2024-04-30/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 19:12:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
