      <title>麥當勞因顧客變得挑剔而出現罕見的利潤下滑</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/mcdonalds-sales-misses-estimates-customers-cut-back-spending-2024-04-30/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[麥當勞兩年來首次未能達到季度利潤預期，因為精打細算的消費者忽視了其優惠，而中東衝突也影響了這家漢堡連鎖店的國際銷售。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/mcdonalds-sales-misses-estimates-customers-cut-back-spending-2024-04-30/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 11:02:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>可口可樂押注昂貴的蘇打水和國際需求以提高年度銷售預期</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/coca-cola-raises-annual-organic-sales-forecast-strong-global-demand-higher-2024-04-30/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[可口可樂在第一季業績超出預期後，週二上調了年度有機銷售預期，因為美國和國際市場的消費者為其昂貴的蘇打水和果汁支付了更多的錢。]]></description>
